2
00:01:23,166 --> 00:01:26,806
<i>...Podoficiru Dzeri S. Rajs,
necasno vas razresavamo.</i>

3
00:01:28,842 --> 00:01:33,592
<i>Odobreno od strane Vrhovnog suda
kao rezultat nalaza grupe oficira...</i>

4
00:02:34,322 --> 00:02:35,362
Tacno u minut.

5
00:02:38,675 --> 00:02:40,418
Vidimo se kasnije, covek.
- Vidimo se.

6
00:02:40,419 --> 00:02:42,749
Dzeri, jebem li ti, dolazi ovamo!

7
00:02:56,660 --> 00:02:58,820
Koliko si propana sinoc prosuo?

8
00:02:59,419 --> 00:03:01,629
Ne secam se.
Pise na papirima.

9
00:03:01,966 --> 00:03:04,726
Proverio sam tezinu.
Manjka ti 130 kilograma.

10
00:03:04,727 --> 00:03:07,757
Dugujes mi 60 dolara.
- Mora da je greska.

11
00:03:08,151 --> 00:03:12,252
Ne, brojke nikad ne lazu.
Lazu samo takvi supci poput tebe.

12
00:03:12,253 --> 00:03:15,983
Sesti put u tri meseca te hvatam
da prosipas propan.

13
00:03:16,382 --> 00:03:19,062
Dosta mi je.
- To je prokleta greska.

14
00:03:19,647 --> 00:03:24,027
Aleks, proveri jos jednom.
- Ne, 60 dolara ti uzimam od plate.

15
00:03:26,909 --> 00:03:32,349
Budi pazljiv, prijatelju moj.
Prijavicu te za kradju ako se jos jednom ponovi.

16
00:03:33,295 --> 00:03:35,505
Vidimo se veceras. Tacno u 21h.

17
00:03:36,089 --> 00:03:37,889
Trebalo bi da bude posla.

18
00:03:38,069 --> 00:03:40,359
Indijanci dobijaju cekove veceras.

19
00:03:40,661 --> 00:03:44,451
Neka frizider bude pun Koka Kole i
rafovi puni cipsa.

20
00:03:44,570 --> 00:03:47,370
Mnogo cemo da zaradimo na tim  sranjima.

21
00:03:51,302 --> 00:03:51,932
Jebi se!

22
00:03:53,263 --> 00:03:54,183
Sta je bilo?

23
00:03:55,357 --> 00:03:56,337
Sta si rekao?

24
00:04:02,900 --> 00:04:03,360
Nista.

25
00:04:04,533 --> 00:04:07,553
Tako sam i mislio.
I ti se jebi, supcino.

26
00:04:08,512 --> 00:04:10,262
Otpusten si, kuckin sine!

27
00:05:36,104 --> 00:05:36,794
Ej, cale!

28
00:05:41,306 --> 00:05:42,056
Ej, momci!

29
00:05:43,154 --> 00:05:45,184
Da li vam je jutros platila?

30
00:05:45,189 --> 00:05:48,629
Da, cale. Sve smo zavrsili.
Dali smo novac mami.

31
00:05:49,978 --> 00:05:51,873
Rekao sam vam da ga date meni.

32
00:05:51,874 --> 00:05:54,904
Izvini cale,
naterala nas je da damo njoj.

33
00:05:56,751 --> 00:05:58,801
Zdravo tata!
- Zdravo lepoto.

34
00:05:59,287 --> 00:06:01,037
Ket kaze: "Zdravo tata!".

35
00:06:01,803 --> 00:06:03,263
Kazi: "Zdravo tata!".

36
00:06:04,409 --> 00:06:08,779
Duso, tata mora da udje u kucu.
- Ket te je pozdravila, tata.

37
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:16,330
Zdravo, Ket.

38
00:06:22,254 --> 00:06:24,700
Je li u redu, duso?
Moze li tata da ide u kucu?

39
00:06:24,701 --> 00:06:25,631
Da.
- Dobro.

40
00:06:40,543 --> 00:06:41,113
Sta je?

41
00:06:42,849 --> 00:06:44,129
Jebo te...
Nista!

42
00:06:45,382 --> 00:06:46,772
Nemoj ti meni tako.

43
00:06:47,687 --> 00:06:49,077
Kako je prosao dan?

44
00:06:51,415 --> 00:06:52,745
Kako se ti osecas?

45
00:06:54,135 --> 00:06:55,525
Sta je Aleks rekao?

46
00:06:59,522 --> 00:06:59,982
Nista.

47
00:07:01,024 --> 00:07:03,001
O, nista. Kaze da...
- Ti meni reci!

48
00:07:03,002 --> 00:07:05,912
Odbice ti  od plate jos 60 dolara, Djeri.

49
00:07:06,842 --> 00:07:10,790
Kaze da si ga opet prevario sinoc
sa propanom. Sta se desava?

50
00:07:10,791 --> 00:07:13,680
Ako te zvao, zasto njega nisi pitala
sta se desava?!

51
00:07:13,681 --> 00:07:17,121
On mene jebe, Nora!
- Da, naravno, on tebe jebe.

52
00:07:18,124 --> 00:07:21,029
Ja sam jebeni lazov, a?
Verujes tom kretenu?

53
00:07:21,030 --> 00:07:22,250
Jebi se, supcino!

54
00:07:28,926 --> 00:07:30,376
Kakvo je ovo sranje?

55
00:07:30,961 --> 00:07:34,401
Racuni koje se jos uvek nisi potrudio
da platis.

56
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:38,346
Cekaj, dao sam ti novac za ovo
prosle nedelje.

57
00:07:38,347 --> 00:07:41,367
To je bilo za nesto drugo.
- Da?! Za sta?

58
00:07:42,566 --> 00:07:45,196
Jebenih 200 dolara!
Jesi li poludela?

59
00:07:46,977 --> 00:07:49,775
Nije to sve moje.
Pricao si sa svojim bratom sat vremena.

60
00:07:49,776 --> 00:07:53,756
Trazio sam mu pozajmicu.
Tvoje je... koliko ...20 dolara?

61
00:07:54,423 --> 00:07:57,928
Boze, sta je 20 dolara?
- Kako mislis sta je 20 dolara?

62
00:07:57,929 --> 00:08:01,009
Imamo cetvoro jebene dece,
treba da sipamo gorivo u auto,

63
00:08:01,010 --> 00:08:05,330
da bacimo hranu na jebeni sto. Razmisljaj!
- U redu, jebi se.

64
00:08:07,977 --> 00:08:11,989
Kako cemo da platimo isporuku?
- To nije moj problem. Snadji se sam.

65
00:08:11,990 --> 00:08:15,093
Da si vise pazio na poslu,
ne bi smo gubili toliko novca.

66
00:08:15,094 --> 00:08:18,609
Znaci ja sam kriv?
Nisam dovoljno bio pazljiv na poslu?!

67
00:08:18,610 --> 00:08:22,450
Radim kao konj za tebe.
Po ceo dan, a dobijam samo...

68
00:08:23,505 --> 00:08:27,203
Ti radis kao konj za mene, a?
Ko vodi brigu o tvojoj deci?

69
00:08:27,204 --> 00:08:29,464
To su nasa deca!
Moja i tvoja!

70
00:08:29,584 --> 00:08:31,417
Ko se brine o njima?
Ja!

71
00:08:31,418 --> 00:08:33,975
Ja se brinem o ovoj rupi u koju si nas
smestio.

72
00:08:33,976 --> 00:08:35,683
Ja sam nas smestio?
- Da ti si.

73
00:08:35,684 --> 00:08:37,722
Ja sam nas smestio ovde,
a ti nemas nista sa svim tim?!

74
00:08:37,723 --> 00:08:40,076
Nemam.
- Znaci samo sam ja kriv?!

75
00:08:40,077 --> 00:08:42,769
Da, za sve si ti kriv,
jer imas psihickih problema.

76
00:08:42,770 --> 00:08:46,090
Mislis da mozes da...
- Jebi se! Sta ti znas?!

77
00:08:47,102 --> 00:08:49,161
Kucko jebena!
- Mamu ti jebem!

78
00:08:49,162 --> 00:08:50,962
Skini mi se.
- Jebem ti!

79
00:08:50,999 --> 00:08:52,219
Da, bezi pickice!

80
00:09:25,623 --> 00:09:27,943
Vecera je za 5 minuta.
U redu?!

81
00:09:29,707 --> 00:09:31,867
Izadji napolje i jebeno pomozi.

82
00:09:35,387 --> 00:09:38,427
Djeri, cujem te kako opet places.
Prestani.

83
00:09:40,122 --> 00:09:42,882
<i>Djeri, prestani odmah?
Izlazi napolje...</i>

84
00:10:13,171 --> 00:10:13,631
Djeri?

85
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:20,230
Prestani da se skrivas i dodji da pomognes.

86
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:23,669
Izlazi napolje i pomozi,
govno jedno.

87
00:10:27,107 --> 00:10:31,667
Opet si isprskao carsave?
Rekla sam ti da to ne moze da se opere.

88
00:10:31,668 --> 00:10:33,762
Ti bas nemas ni malo postovanja prema meni.

89
00:10:33,763 --> 00:10:35,403
Ne koristi...
- Odjebi!

90
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:38,069
Uzmi tolet papir.
Nemas jos puno.

91
00:10:40,008 --> 00:10:42,278
I pocisti kad zavrsis.
Ja necu!

92
00:10:44,063 --> 00:10:44,813
O, sranje!

93
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:16,450
Ej, klinci, vreme je za jelo!

94
00:11:27,146 --> 00:11:28,436
Izvinite, vrata...!

95
00:11:38,414 --> 00:11:39,634
Pokazite mi ruke!

96
00:11:40,585 --> 00:11:42,969
Ciste su, mama.
- Stivi, nemoj da mi odgovaras.

97
00:11:42,970 --> 00:11:45,300
Samo mi pokazi ruke.
- Ciste su.

98
00:11:46,386 --> 00:11:49,186
Moje ruke su ciste.
- Dobro. Sedi dole.

99
00:11:51,926 --> 00:11:53,556
Gde je tata?
- Dolazi.

100
00:11:55,509 --> 00:11:56,729
Djeri, cekamo te!

101
00:11:59,481 --> 00:12:00,751
Je l' tata dobro?

102
00:12:03,011 --> 00:12:03,471
Supak.

103
00:12:06,308 --> 00:12:07,588
Ovo predugo traje.

104
00:12:11,427 --> 00:12:13,093
Tako je kilav.
- Tacno.

105
00:12:13,094 --> 00:12:14,434
Nije.
- Da, jeste.

106
00:12:16,476 --> 00:12:17,866
Svaki dan je ovako.

107
00:13:16,488 --> 00:13:16,948
Hajde.

108
00:14:08,545 --> 00:14:11,285
Izvini, tata.
Nisam hteo da te ljutim.

109
00:14:13,815 --> 00:14:15,435
Ne brini za to.
Jedi.

110
00:14:24,639 --> 00:14:26,439
Dodji sedi sa nama, mama.

111
00:14:28,714 --> 00:14:29,694
Jedi tu, Rej.

112
00:15:57,622 --> 00:15:58,302
8:30 je!

113
00:16:00,470 --> 00:16:02,230
Hajde, ustaj.
Zakasnices.

114
00:18:44,278 --> 00:18:45,028
Hej, Lui!?

115
00:18:58,134 --> 00:18:58,534
Lui?!

116
00:19:15,869 --> 00:19:16,619
Sta radis?

117
00:19:19,656 --> 00:19:22,863
Zar ti smena ne pocinje od 9?
Sta radis ovde tako rano?

118
00:19:22,864 --> 00:19:25,124
Lui, pitao sam te sta to radis?

119
00:19:26,615 --> 00:19:27,725
Radim.
- Radis?

120
00:19:28,368 --> 00:19:31,155
Ovde nema nikoga.
- Djeri, covece, radim...

121
00:19:31,156 --> 00:19:33,086
Naravno da radis.
Pusacu...

122
00:19:35,467 --> 00:19:37,207
Sta to jebeno radis?
A?

123
00:19:37,517 --> 00:19:39,137
Dizi se!
- Zao mi je.

124
00:19:40,076 --> 00:19:41,466
Mene jebes, Lui, a?

125
00:19:42,029 --> 00:19:43,899
Nije moja krivica.
- Dole!

126
00:19:46,617 --> 00:19:47,837
Ubice me, covece.

127
00:19:52,242 --> 00:19:54,222
Mene jebes, a?
Kuckin sine.

128
00:19:55,996 --> 00:19:56,746
Ne, Djeri.

129
00:19:57,942 --> 00:20:00,032
Aleks me naterao.
Zao mi je.

130
00:20:03,452 --> 00:20:05,473
Otpustio bi me da nisam to uradio.

131
00:20:05,474 --> 00:20:06,224
Imam dete.

132
00:20:07,761 --> 00:20:10,781
Ne smem da izgubim ovaj posao.
Zao mi je.

133
00:20:11,023 --> 00:20:12,243
Jebes to, covece.

134
00:20:13,061 --> 00:20:14,391
Pazio sam te, Lui!

135
00:20:15,220 --> 00:20:16,820
Cuvao te!
Ti mi jebeno zabi u ledja!

136
00:20:16,821 --> 00:20:18,971
Sta sam drugo mogao da uradim?

137
00:20:20,261 --> 00:20:21,541
Nisam imao izbora.

138
00:20:25,659 --> 00:20:26,059
Bezi.

139
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:27,660
Bezi!

140
00:20:30,197 --> 00:20:32,057
Bezi odavde.
- Zao mi je.

141
00:20:40,145 --> 00:20:40,945
Zao mi je!

142
00:25:23,801 --> 00:25:27,131
Hej, cale, hoces li uzeti ranije novine
jutros?

143
00:25:32,189 --> 00:25:34,699
Idemo da se spremimo.
- Gladan sam.

144
00:25:34,814 --> 00:25:35,214
Cuti.

145
00:25:56,830 --> 00:25:58,530
Sacekacemo napolju, cale.

146
00:26:51,099 --> 00:26:52,499
Dobro jutro, tatice.

147
00:27:41,516 --> 00:27:41,916
Halo.

148
00:27:42,816 --> 00:27:43,336
<i>Dzeri?!</i>

149
00:27:44,597 --> 00:27:45,227
Nije on.

150
00:27:45,697 --> 00:27:47,377
<i>Gde je Djeri, jebem ti?</i>

151
00:27:48,274 --> 00:27:48,817
Ne znam...

152
00:27:48,818 --> 00:27:49,278
<i>Seres!</i>

153
00:27:52,620 --> 00:27:53,200
Supcino.

154
00:27:59,602 --> 00:28:00,412
Stivi? Rej?

155
00:28:03,073 --> 00:28:04,643
Vreme je za ustajanje.

156
00:28:19,453 --> 00:28:19,973
Sranje.

157
00:28:28,557 --> 00:28:29,247
Jebem ti.

158
00:28:48,937 --> 00:28:51,087
Sta ti radis budan ovako rano?

159
00:28:54,427 --> 00:28:55,237
Hoces kafu?

160
00:28:58,594 --> 00:29:00,864
To je Aleks.
Vristi trazeci te.

161
00:29:03,267 --> 00:29:04,077
Hoces li...

162
00:29:06,217 --> 00:29:06,617
Halo.

163
00:29:07,105 --> 00:29:08,836
<i>Je l' taj jebeni glupak tu?</i>

164
00:29:08,837 --> 00:29:10,287
Jeste.
Sta je bilo?

165
00:29:10,407 --> 00:29:11,747
<i>Skroz me opeljesio.</i>

166
00:29:12,986 --> 00:29:16,126
<i>Pumpe su prazne, alat je nestao,
roba mi je nestala.</i>

167
00:29:16,127 --> 00:29:17,167
<i>Unistio me je!</i>

168
00:29:17,698 --> 00:29:19,553
Sta si to, jebote, uradio?

169
00:29:19,554 --> 00:29:21,174
Da li si ga opljackao?

170
00:29:21,467 --> 00:29:22,787
<i>Ne daj mu da ode.</i>

171
00:29:23,211 --> 00:29:23,901
Ne, necu.

172
00:29:24,371 --> 00:29:26,701
<i>Beskorisno govno.
Sta je s njim?</i>

173
00:29:28,120 --> 00:29:29,500
Ne znam sta mu je.

174
00:29:30,863 --> 00:29:31,961
Mozda su ga sjebali?!

175
00:29:31,962 --> 00:29:34,626
<i>Jebem li mu majku,
ocisticu sobu s njim.</i>

176
00:29:34,627 --> 00:29:36,174
Trebao si da poginjes tamo.

177
00:29:36,175 --> 00:29:38,555
Bilo bi nam mnogo bolje bez tebe.

178
00:29:47,433 --> 00:29:47,833
Tata?

179
00:29:51,825 --> 00:29:52,755
Nemoj tatice!

180
00:29:53,621 --> 00:29:53,901
Ne!

181
00:29:59,726 --> 00:30:00,946
Molim te, tatice!

182
00:30:01,949 --> 00:30:03,579
Molim te nemoj, tatice.

183
00:30:18,753 --> 00:30:19,563
Nemoj tata!

184
00:30:20,572 --> 00:30:21,792
Nemoj.
Volim te.

185
00:32:09,605 --> 00:32:10,355
Obuci ovo.

186
00:32:15,427 --> 00:32:15,887
Hajde.

187
00:32:53,788 --> 00:32:57,288
Moracu da prevarim ljude koji me traze.
- U redu.

188
00:33:05,243 --> 00:33:05,823
Spremna?

189
00:33:06,863 --> 00:33:07,733
Jesam, tata.

190
00:33:13,842 --> 00:33:14,302
Dobro.

191
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:56,730
Stegni jako.

192
00:40:40,449 --> 00:40:43,759
Auto put je na oko 3 kilometra u
onom pravcu.

193
00:40:46,192 --> 00:40:47,592
Tamo ima prodavnica.

194
00:40:49,416 --> 00:40:53,896
Za tebe je to mnogo da pesacis
pa je najbolje da sacekas ovde.

195
00:40:54,514 --> 00:40:58,114
Donecu nam nesto za jelo.
Vraticu se za 5-6 sati.

196
00:41:04,793 --> 00:41:06,243
Hoces li se vratiti?

197
00:41:18,636 --> 00:41:21,896
Bez obzira sta se desilo,
vraticu se po tebe.

198
00:41:24,375 --> 00:41:25,415
Znam da hoces.

199
00:41:26,654 --> 00:41:28,334
Uvek se vratis po mene.

200
00:41:32,950 --> 00:41:34,170
Vidimo se uskoro.

201
00:42:34,243 --> 00:42:35,403
Volim te tatice.

202
00:42:37,045 --> 00:42:38,205
Volim te tatice.

203
00:44:17,296 --> 00:44:19,286
<i>Americki vojnik ubio porodicu</i>

204
00:44:23,965 --> 00:44:25,825
Uzecu i novine.
- U redu.

205
00:44:28,324 --> 00:44:29,304
Ukupno 87,50.

206
00:44:45,786 --> 00:44:47,416
Hvala.
- Nema na cemu.

207
00:45:05,107 --> 00:45:06,267
Volim te tatice.

208
00:45:46,280 --> 00:45:48,020
Molim te Boze, neka odu.

209
00:45:49,559 --> 00:45:50,249
Molim te.

210
00:46:05,093 --> 00:46:06,893
Molim te Boze.
Molim te.

211
00:47:26,306 --> 00:47:28,286
Uspelo je.
Pomolila sam se.

212
00:47:29,579 --> 00:47:31,139
Bog je ucinio da odu.

213
00:47:32,217 --> 00:47:36,467
Mogu sve da ucinim da bude dobro.
Samo moram da se pomolim.

214
00:48:22,342 --> 00:48:23,032
Molim te.

215
00:48:27,851 --> 00:48:28,541
Molim te.

216
00:48:30,498 --> 00:48:32,068
Molim te neka proradi.

217
00:48:34,397 --> 00:48:34,917
Probaj.

218
00:48:39,963 --> 00:48:40,543
Sacekaj.

219
00:48:43,451 --> 00:48:44,501
Pokusaj ponovo.

220
00:49:00,882 --> 00:49:04,136
Opet sam se pomolila.
I bog je ucinio da radi.

221
00:49:04,137 --> 00:49:05,177
Jesi li video?

222
00:49:07,613 --> 00:49:08,363
Da, jesam.

223
00:49:28,150 --> 00:49:30,830
<i>Dobro jutro i hvala sto slusate CTT...</i>

224
00:49:38,837 --> 00:49:40,297
<i>Evo poslednjih vesti.</i>

225
00:49:41,211 --> 00:49:45,590
<i>Potraga za rezervistom Djerijem S. Rajsom
i njegovom cerkom Selinom se nastavlja.</i>

226
00:49:45,591 --> 00:49:49,391
<i>Njegova trudna zena Nora i dvoje dece
su pronadjeni...</i>

227
00:50:58,536 --> 00:51:01,589
Ako te ista bude pitao,
secas se sta treba da kazes?

228
00:51:01,590 --> 00:51:05,950
Na putu smo za Kanadu.
Idemo u posetu baki jer je u bolnicu.

229
00:51:17,794 --> 00:51:20,714
Znam. Kakva je razlika?
Domace je domace.

230
00:51:20,913 --> 00:51:23,463
J, MJ, KJB...
meni je to sve isto.

231
00:51:26,062 --> 00:51:26,992
Sacekaj malo.

232
00:51:34,586 --> 00:51:35,216
Kako je?

233
00:51:37,000 --> 00:51:37,460
Dobro.

234
00:51:40,175 --> 00:51:41,915
Mozes li da je popravis?

235
00:51:42,033 --> 00:51:43,893
Koliko dugo vozis na njoj?

236
00:51:44,370 --> 00:51:45,470
Oko 800 metara.

237
00:51:50,508 --> 00:51:52,368
Bice da si iskrivio felnu.

238
00:51:53,992 --> 00:51:55,442
Da, mislim da jesam.

239
00:51:55,825 --> 00:51:57,215
Gde ti je rezervna?

240
00:51:57,554 --> 00:51:58,244
Nemam je.

241
00:52:02,061 --> 00:52:04,501
Sta je ovo?
Pontijak iz '83, '84?

242
00:52:05,052 --> 00:52:05,392
'83.

243
00:52:06,906 --> 00:52:09,491
Lacito ima otpad starih vozila.
Mozda tamo ima nesto za tebe.

244
00:52:09,492 --> 00:52:10,942
Ali ne radi utorkom.

245
00:52:11,111 --> 00:52:15,721
Moraces da se vratis ujutro.
Mozda mogu da iskopam nesto za tebe.

246
00:52:17,905 --> 00:52:21,995
Imas dole niz ulicu mesto gde da prespavas.
- Zvuci dobro.

247
00:52:22,778 --> 00:52:25,878
Parkiraj auto tamo i
ostavi kljuceve unutra.

248
00:53:10,329 --> 00:53:11,669
Posle tebe, tatice.

249
00:53:13,171 --> 00:53:13,751
Sacekaj.

250
00:53:15,024 --> 00:53:17,404
Hvala ti Boze na ovoj lepoj sobi.

251
00:53:20,842 --> 00:53:22,412
Sada mozemo da udjemo.

252
00:53:56,801 --> 00:54:01,605
<i>Forenzicari su uvereni da ce tela gospodina i
njegove cerke biti nadjeni</i>

253
00:54:01,606 --> 00:54:05,046
<i>negde uz obalu te reke
u narednih nekoliko dana.</i>

254
00:54:05,732 --> 00:54:10,992
<i>Nakon skoro deset dana ocajne i opsezne
potrage za Rajsom i cerkom Selinom,</i>

255
00:54:11,804 --> 00:54:16,754
<i>sledeci otkrice brutalno ubistvo Rajsove
trudne zene Nore i njegova dva sina,</i>

256
00:54:16,755 --> 00:54:21,895
<i>Stiven i Rej, ova prica se priblizava tragicnom
epilogu koje se, cini se,</i>

257
00:54:22,741 --> 00:54:25,791
<i>samoubistvo gospodina Rajsa i
njegove cerke.</i>

258
00:54:25,916 --> 00:54:30,366
<i>Vojni zvanicnici su potvrdili da je
gosp. Rajs otpusten pre tri meseca..</i>

259
00:54:30,367 --> 00:54:35,551
<i>Nakon incidenta u kom su on i njegovi saborci
bili umesani u MI-LA masakru u</i>

260
00:54:35,552 --> 00:54:36,662
<i>okolini Faludze.</i>

261
00:54:37,260 --> 00:54:41,540
<i>Pentagon i Stejt Dept. odbijaju da komentarisu
tekucu istragu.</i>

262
00:54:42,344 --> 00:54:46,014
<i>MI-LA masakr se dogodio u Vijetnamu
16. marta 1968.</i>

263
00:54:47,605 --> 00:54:53,045
<i>Do danas, incidenti u kojima su americki vojnici
poslati da ubiju 347 nevinih,</i>

264
00:54:53,772 --> 00:54:56,422
<i>nenaoruzanih ljudi ostaje nerazjasnjeno.</i>

265
00:54:58,126 --> 00:55:03,396
<i>G.Rajs je navodni samoubica koji prati trend
rezervista povratnika iz Iraka.</i>

266
00:55:04,481 --> 00:55:07,299
<i>Neki pronalaze poslove u kojima ih
nelegalno odbijaju.</i>

267
00:55:07,300 --> 00:55:09,942
<i>Porodice im se suocavaju sa
financijskom propascu.</i>

268
00:55:09,943 --> 00:55:12,110
<i>Mnogi su u nemogucnosti da imaju
normalan socijalan zivot.</i>

269
00:55:12,111 --> 00:55:16,387
<i>Neki pate od stresnog posttraumatskog
poremecaja koje se okrece prema nasilju</i>

270
00:55:16,388 --> 00:55:19,608
<i>prema svojim porodicama i
prema samima sebi...</i>

271
00:55:33,709 --> 00:55:35,089
Sta je to maj-laj?

272
00:55:41,991 --> 00:55:42,501
MI-LA.

273
00:55:45,350 --> 00:55:47,090
To je mesto u Vijetnamu.

274
00:55:47,742 --> 00:55:49,722
Mesto na drugom kraju sveta.

275
00:55:53,308 --> 00:55:54,458
Tamo si ti bio?

276
00:55:56,763 --> 00:55:57,043
Ne.

277
00:55:59,402 --> 00:56:00,842
Ja sam bio u Iraku.

278
00:56:04,712 --> 00:56:07,142
Da li si ubio puno ljudi u Iraku?

279
00:56:13,113 --> 00:56:13,573
Nisam.

280
00:56:15,933 --> 00:56:17,503
Ovo je bilo drugacije.

281
00:56:19,716 --> 00:56:21,816
Nikad nisam uradio tako nesto.

282
00:56:51,378 --> 00:56:52,818
Da li si ubio mamu?

283
00:56:57,017 --> 00:56:57,477
Jesam.

284
00:57:02,228 --> 00:57:04,368
Da li si ubio Stivija i Reja?

285
00:57:07,955 --> 00:57:08,415
Jesam.

286
00:57:10,529 --> 00:57:11,799
Zasto si ih ubio?

287
00:57:15,982 --> 00:57:17,142
Povredili su me.

288
00:57:20,096 --> 00:57:21,366
Mi smo te voleli.

289
00:57:27,700 --> 00:57:28,330
Da znam.

290
00:57:31,798 --> 00:57:33,658
Ali to nije bilo dovoljno.

291
00:57:35,130 --> 00:57:36,940
Bol nikako nije prestajao.

292
00:57:39,165 --> 00:57:40,025
A ja, tata?

293
00:57:42,082 --> 00:57:43,002
Ja te volim.

294
00:57:45,081 --> 00:57:46,641
Da li je to dovoljno?

295
00:57:51,460 --> 00:57:51,740
Da.

296
00:57:53,043 --> 00:57:53,913
Duso, jeste.

297
00:57:56,368 --> 00:57:58,288
Jesi li jos uvek povredjen?

298
00:58:03,986 --> 00:58:05,256
Ne na isti nacin.

299
00:58:17,603 --> 00:58:21,953
Kada bi se mama i Stivi i Rej vratili,
da li bi bio srecan?

300
00:58:30,774 --> 00:58:31,874
Naravno da bih.

301
00:58:37,099 --> 00:58:39,189
Neka se vrate, molim te Boze,

302
00:58:41,442 --> 00:58:42,482
neka se vrate.

303
01:00:22,975 --> 01:00:23,965
<i>Potreban kuvar</i>

304
01:00:58,047 --> 01:00:59,437
Ovde si zbog posla?

305
01:01:00,624 --> 01:01:01,794
Posao?
Mislis...

306
01:01:02,180 --> 01:01:03,980
Imam jedan da ti ponudim.

307
01:01:05,164 --> 01:01:09,184
Ne. Ja ustvari trazim posao,
ali sam samo dosao na kafu.

308
01:01:10,388 --> 01:01:11,138
Sta radis?

309
01:01:13,609 --> 01:01:14,829
Ja sam mehanicar.

310
01:01:15,805 --> 01:01:17,588
Niko ovde ne trazi mehanicara.

311
01:01:17,589 --> 01:01:21,559
Ovde je jedino potreban radnik,
ali samo za jedno mesto.

312
01:01:23,342 --> 01:01:24,792
Znas da skuvas jaje?

313
01:01:27,299 --> 01:01:29,519
Naravno.
- Onda si dobio posao.

314
01:01:29,604 --> 01:01:31,822
Ako hoces.
Placa se 10 dolara na sat.

315
01:01:31,823 --> 01:01:33,283
Bolje nego minimalac.

316
01:01:33,348 --> 01:01:35,693
Smena je od 6 ujutro do 6 popodne.

317
01:01:35,694 --> 01:01:36,564
Dovrsi kafu.

318
01:01:37,067 --> 01:01:41,317
Ako to nije najbolja kafa koju si pio,
mozes da me odbijes.

319
01:02:06,298 --> 01:02:07,278
Rekla sam ti.

320
01:02:08,316 --> 01:02:09,836
Pocinjes ujutro.
Oli!

321
01:02:11,641 --> 01:02:12,161
Dzordz.

322
01:02:13,792 --> 01:02:16,582
Drago mi je da sam te upoznala, Dzordz.

323
01:02:16,825 --> 01:02:19,095
Ne, ja castim.
Vidimo se sutra.

324
01:02:19,232 --> 01:02:19,692
Dobro.

325
01:03:30,330 --> 01:03:32,140
Ej, lepi.
- Zdravo, tata.

326
01:03:33,548 --> 01:03:35,298
Jesi li gladna?
- Jesam.

327
01:03:39,995 --> 01:03:43,764
Kupio sam neke stvarcice.
- Mogu li da spremim veceru?

328
01:03:43,765 --> 01:03:44,515
Da, mozes.

329
01:04:22,493 --> 01:04:26,673
Hvala ti Boze na ovom obroku i
hvala ti sto si me slusao.

330
01:04:28,061 --> 01:04:32,893
Bog hoce da se molim svaki dan
dok se mama i Stivi i Rej ne vrate.

331
01:04:32,894 --> 01:04:34,584
To ce biti iznenadjenje.

332
01:04:46,854 --> 01:04:48,934
Je l' ti se ne svidja, tata?

333
01:05:01,320 --> 01:05:02,010
Dobro je.

334
01:05:12,061 --> 01:05:13,981
Ovo izgleda kao lep gradic.

335
01:05:18,863 --> 01:05:20,613
Ostacemo ovde neko vreme.

336
01:05:25,833 --> 01:05:27,403
Danas sam dobio posao.

337
01:05:37,202 --> 01:05:40,932
Duso, moraces da ostanes unutra dok
sam ja na poslu.

338
01:05:41,471 --> 01:05:44,527
To znaci da ne mozes napolje kad nisam tu.
Moras da ostanes unutra.

339
01:05:44,528 --> 01:05:47,148
Tako te niko nece primetiti.
U redu?

340
01:05:50,780 --> 01:05:51,350
U redu.

341
01:06:31,110 --> 01:06:35,470
Ja sam u sobi 456.
Samo da te obavestim da cemo ostati ovde.

342
01:06:36,533 --> 01:06:38,853
U redu.
Svidja ti se ovo mesto?

343
01:06:39,288 --> 01:06:39,978
Dobro je.

344
01:06:55,737 --> 01:06:57,547
Treba mi tri porudzbine...

345
01:07:01,199 --> 01:07:01,889
Mozes li?

346
01:07:06,272 --> 01:07:06,792
Sranje.

347
01:08:08,929 --> 01:08:09,449
Sranje.

348
01:09:08,091 --> 01:09:08,491
Tata!

